name: ouroboros (itch) (Duckbeanpotato)
description:
WASD to move, R to restart

Description
You are an ouroboros who loves to eat your own tail! You also LOVE eating people!

But there are obstacles in your way...

Traverse around barriers and eat snacks (civilians) on your journey to your tail in this slithery top-down puzzle game.

Made for Brackeys Game Jam 2023.1 in ~4 days

Credits
Kevin Wei, Dylan DeCastro, Heyman Luong
